Installation Instructions
=========================

1. Edit configurable settings in Makefile if needed, or simply
   override the defaults when invoking make.

2. Build and install the software.

   make
   make install

   This installs the following files:
   /lib/modules/<kernel-version>/kernel/extra/pppol2tp.ko
   /usr/lib/pppol2tp-kmod/...

   To install under a different root directory, say /tmp, use

   make install DESTDIR=/tmp

   To cross-compile, define CROSS_COMPILE to be the tool prefix, e.g.

   make CROSS_COMPILE=ppc_7xx-

Reporting problems
==================

Please report problems to openl2tp-users@lists.sourceforge.net or
raise a bug at sourceforge.net/projects/openl2tp.


